<item>
            <title>[LU-19456] lbuild: sles15sp7 should be supported</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19456</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;There is a line in `contrib/lbuild/lbuild` that looks like: `location=&quot;https://linux.mellanox.com/public/repo/doca/${DOCA_VERSION}/SOURCES/MLNX_OFED&quot;`
	&lt;ol&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;The MLNX_OFED needs to be lowercase when the doca version is 3.1.0: &lt;a href=&quot;https://linux.mellanox.com/public/repo/doca/3.1.0/SOURCES/mlnx_ofed/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://linux.mellanox.com/public/repo/doca/3.1.0/SOURCES/mlnx_ofed/&lt;/a&gt; vs &lt;a href=&quot;https://linux.mellanox.com/public/repo/doca/3.1.0/SOURCES/MLNX_OFED/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://linux.mellanox.com/public/repo/doca/3.1.0/SOURCES/MLNX_OFED/&lt;/a&gt; (The second one with capital is giving not found error)
		&lt;ol&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;For other current lower versions, MLNX_OFED is capitalized: &lt;a href=&quot;https://linux.mellanox.com/public/repo/doca/2.9.3/SOURCES/MLNX_OFED/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://linux.mellanox.com/public/repo/doca/2.9.3/SOURCES/MLNX_OFED/&lt;/a&gt; vs &lt;a href=&quot;https://linux.mellanox.com/public/repo/doca/2.9.3/SOURCES/mlnx_ofed/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://linux.mellanox.com/public/repo/doca/2.9.3/SOURCES/mlnx_ofed/&lt;/a&gt; (This time the second one with lower case is giving not found errors)&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ol&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ol&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;We need to add `&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;&#8220;3.1.0&#8221;&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;=&#8220;0.9.7.0&#8221;` to the `doca_version_map` for sles15sp7&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;For branch b_es6_0, on line 1896 it goes into the same case block for mlnx and doca, but for the b_es7_0 branch the same code on line 1892 shows the doca case statement has its own block and is causing the build to fail for `sles15sp7` builds. It is changing the sles15sp7 to sles15u7. I think this is correct for rhel builds, but it shouldn&apos;t be doing that for sles builds&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
</description>
